# Eliminate Mock Data Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
The objective is to eliminate the use of mock data in all interfaces across the Smart HR Performance Management System. This involves updating frontend adapters to connect to backend APIs, and updating backend controllers/services to fetch data from PostgreSQL (using Drizzle ORM) instead of returning hardcoded values. Finally, missing or conflicting processes will be documented in `docs/process-analysis.md`.

## User Review Required
> [!CAUTION]
> Removing mock data requires writing raw DB queries and aggregations for complex features like Fairness Analysis and ML Turnover Predictions. If exact algorithms run out of scope, basic SQL aggregations will be used as the source of truth, but they may differ from previous static mock numbers.

## Proposed Changes

### Frontend Adapters & Stores
- **[client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/alert.store.ts)**
  - **[MODIFY]**: Remove `MOCK_ALERTS`, `MOCK_EXPLANATIONS`, `MOCK_RECOMMENDATIONS`.
  - Update `useAlertStore` to make HTTP calls to `/api/alerts` using Axios/fetch.
- **[client/src/stores/business/case.store.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/stores/business/case.store.ts)**
  - **[MODIFY]**: Remove `mockCases`. Connect to actual Cases API (if available, otherwise rely on local state syncing to the backend).
- **[client/src/services/adapters/dashboardDataAdapter.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/adapters/dashboardDataAdapter.ts)**
  - **[MODIFY]**: Remove `mockKPIs`, `mockRiskData`, `mockPerformanceData`, `mockFairnessData`, `mockFeedItems`.
  - Make HTTP call to `/api/dashboard/stats`.
- **[client/src/services/resources/profileDataAdapter.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/resources/profileDataAdapter.ts)**
  - **[MODIFY]**: Remove logic that generates random predictive data based on ID seed. Call `/api/employees/:id/profile` bundle endpoint.

